Name: Brains
Title: Brains
Description: Warmz is learning about when you go to bed and what helps you sleep well. It optimizes and make suggestions for you.

Name: Safety
Title: Safety
Description: Thanks to the smarts embedded inside warmz, it will safely shutdown if it detects an error or hazard to you.

Name: Smart Schedules
Title: Smart Schedules
Description: Thanks to the smarts, your bed will know when you're home and when it is cold outside. Resulting in the perfect night's sleep.

Name: Sensors
Title: Sensors
Description: Imbedded with miniscule temperature sensors, you don't need to worry about waking up sweaty as warmz will regulate your temperature.

Name: smart speaker
Title: Voice Assistant Integration
Description: With integration into Alexa and Google Home, you can warm up the bed without having to get out of it.

Name: Wifi
Title: Wifi Enabled
Description: With wifi and bluetooth connectivity, your bed will warm up intelligently.

Name: Wire
Title: Thin Wires
Description: The mattress pad has the thinnest wires on the market at safe voltages.

Name: Zones
Title: No More Cold Feet
Description: With up to four different zones, two on each side, you'll never need to worry about the icy touch of cold feet.
